name: Warp Speed
overview:
Your mission is to pilot your spacecraft through a dangerous sector of space and travel the maximum possible distance in the time allotted. You must avoid the planetoids, but passing through the black holes will increase your score by 100.000 parsecs. This was an unreleased prototype.
Warp Speed was to be a 3-D space war prototype game. Made it as far as focus testing. The base code and controller of this game were used in the production of Star Wars instead.
